Program: Thinking Allowed
Title: Working class alienation - Nottingham council estate
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01jhdh1
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 11 Jun 2012
Laurie Taylor explores new research from this year's British Sociological Association conference. Lisa Mckenzie describes the growth in working class alienation on the St Anne's housing estate in Nottingham. Also, Dr Maria Papapolydorou, considers how class impacts on young peoples choice and experience of friendship. Producer: Jayne Egerton. Show less